    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "STR timeout"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "现象：进入STR失败，走了休眠唤醒的唤醒流程"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "原因： STR_MODE没有拉高导致SCC侧LCM认为STR超时，后续SOC走了下电冷起的过程"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "LOG："
    },
    {
