      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20analyze%20kind%20of%20LCM%20issues%20--example%20by%20Chery%208155/image-2024-11-11_13-11-58.png?api=v2",
