    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "措施：转给SOC 继续分析。"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "STR failed"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "现象：进入STR失败，走了休眠唤醒的唤醒流程"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "原因： SOC主动退出STR，后续SOC走了下电冷起的过程"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "LOG："
    },
