      "items": [
        "Voltage issue"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "现象：实车报告仪表大屏黑屏重启"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "原因：实车电源电压出现波动，超高压（＞18.7V）导致SOC请求车机重启。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "LOG："
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/How%20to%20analyze%20kind%20of%20LCM%20issues%20--example%20by%20Chery%208155/image-2024-11-11_13-16-23.png?api=v2",
